title: Jodie Comer | Trump Dodges Questions on Mueller, Tax Returns, WikiLeaks: A Closer Look
description:
Seth takes a closer look at the president resisting calls to release his tax returns and calling the people who investigate him traitors.

Then, Jodie Comer talks about the return of Killing Eve, introducing her parents to Michael Palin and her love of Bruce Springsteen. She also takes a few more questions backstage at Studio 8G.
